g\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e7e519c339b338286aa83b140f369c548d3b2f","tid":350053,"uid":121075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有野要報驚？</blockquote><br />\n咁又無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔開心左好耐<br />\n同埋因爲咁而成日覺得好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8eae0f6f9d4fa90edb438993075b583e81b36cf","tid":350053,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有野要報驚？</blockquote><br />\n咁又無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔開心左好耐<br />\n同埋因爲咁而成日覺得好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n社工係用黎報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n社工要就有咩  個個都走晒去做其他野交數<br />\n生命熱線果類電話有幾可真係有人聽"},{"pid":"388db060cf32d6d45a3f6948921bce57f225a135","tid":350053,"uid":11560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得自己唔識講野 處處得罪人<br />\n因為人際關係俾自己好大壓力 有無人可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過社工同輔導<br />\n我覺得見輔導好啲<br />\n我見開果間收費唔貴，平過睇診所醫生<br />\n有需要嘅話介紹你去睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/piggiepig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpiggiepig&d=%2BbNNOIDYeHgad%2F0WfzAweCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d6c1bf6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/piggiepig</a>"},{"pid":"e6155bcbcee28b09854969635ec7e39e0621bebb","tid":350053,"uid":13885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想屌女社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmo